From 37deb2aeca2288b4868529523f3d9ac45659f412 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
Date: Sun, 8 Feb 2026 22:19:53 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] soc: hpe: add GXP SoC infrastructure drivers

Add the core HPE GXP BMC SoC drivers: gxp-soclib shared library,
gxp-csm, gxp-xreg (150 GPIO lines), gxp-fn2 (power state GPIOs).
Include gxp-regs.h with named register constants.

Co-developed-by: Gilbert Chen <gilbert.chen@hpe.com>
Signed-off-by: Gilbert Chen <gilbert.chen@hpe.com>
Signed-off-by: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
---
